29 case class AddBytes(namespace:String, key:String, value:Array[Byte])

37 
38 /**
39  * TODO: The Caching components are older components which currently do not adhere to the pattern established
40  * for components, so this would most likely at some point need to be rebuilt
41  *
42  * Interface trait that handles the messaging for any caching classes. Then the user would just need to implement
43  * the internal functions
44  */
45 abstract class Cache(name:String) extends Component(name) {
46 
47   import context.dispatcher
48 
49   override def receive = super.receive orElse {
50     case CreateCache(config) => sender ! createCache(config)
51     case DeleteCache(namespace) => sender ! deleteCache(namespace)
52     case Get(namespace, key) => pipe(get(namespace, key)) to sender
53     case AddBytes(namespace, key, value) =>
54       val buffer = ChannelBuffers.wrappedBuffer(value)
55       pipe(add(namespace, key, buffer)) to sender
56     case Add(namespace, key, value) => pipe(add(namespace, key, value)) to sender
57     case Delete(namespace, key) => pipe(delete(namespace, key)) to sender
58     case Decrement(namespace, key, decrementBy) => pipe(decrement(namespace, key, decrementBy)) to sender
59     case Increment(namespace, key, incrementBy) => pipe(increment(namespace, key, incrementBy)) to sender
60     case Contains(namespace, key) => pipe(contains(namespace, key)) to sender
61     case Clear(namespace) => pipe(clear(namespace)) to sender
62   }
63 
64   // Functions to implement for any cache managers using the ICache interface
65   /**
66    * Creates a cache based on the implementer of the function. So could be any cache type
67    *
68    * @param config The
69    * @return
70    */
71   protected def createCache(config:CacheConfig) : Boolean
72   protected def deleteCache(namespace:String) : Boolean
73   protected def get(namespace:String, key:String) : Future[Option[ChannelBuffer]]
74   protected def add(namespace:String, key:String, value:ChannelBuffer) : Future[Boolean]
75   protected def delete(namespace:String, key:String) : Future[Boolean]
76   protected def increment(namespace:String, key:String, incrementBy:Long) : Future[Option[Long]]
77   protected def decrement(namespace:String, key:String, decrementBy:Long) : Future[Option[Long]]
78   protected def contains(namespace:String, key:String) : Future[Boolean]
79   protected def clear(namespace:String) : Future[Boolean]
80 }
